---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import PageTitle from '../../components/PageTitle.astro';
import Card from '../../components/Card.astro';
const classInnerList = 'space-y-2 list-disc';
---

<BaseLayout>
  <div class="flex flex-col items-center px-2 md:px-6 gap-5 md:gap-8 mt-6">
    <PageTitle>About Us</PageTitle>
    <Card class="space-y-8 py-6">
      <div
        class="md:text-lg md:max-w-3xl px-4 leading-relaxed space-y-4"
      >
        <p>
          At Frontier, we believe in making athletes faster, stronger, and more
          powerful. We focus on understanding and improving the body—how it
          moves, adapts, and performs—while asking thoughtful questions of our
          athletes to help them discover their potential. Through education and
          tailored guidance, we create the foundation needed to refine skills
          and achieve peak performance.
        </p>
        <p>
          At the heart of Frontier Sports Performance is a simple truth:
          greatness begins with a foundation of physical and mental resilience.
          Founded by Steven Baron and Jonathan Locher, Frontier Sports
          Performance is the culmination of a lifelong journey in athletics,
          fueled by lessons learned on and off the field.
        </p>
        <p>
          Frontier Sports Performance empowers athletes to push limits, achieve
          breakthroughs, and become stronger in every way.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="space-y-4">
        <h1 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-semibold text-center">
          Our Values
        </h1>
        <div
          class="md:text-lg md:max-w-3xl px-4 leading-relaxed space-y-4"
        >
          <ul
            class:list={[
              classInnerList,
              'md:text-lg list-none space-y-4',
            ]}
          >
            <li>
              <span class="font-bold">Resilience:</span> Building mental and physical
              strength to overcome challenges on and off the field.
            </li>
            <li>
              <span class="font-bold">Discipline:</span>
              Emphasizing consistent effort and focus to achieve lasting results.
            </li>
            <li>
              <span class="font-bold">Empowerment:</span>
              Encouraging athletes to push their limits and unlock their true potential.
            </li>
            <li>
              <span class="font-bold">Innovation:</span>
              Integrating proven methods with forward-thinking approaches to maximize
              performance.
            </li>
            <li>
              <span class="font-bold">Integrity:</span>
              Maintaining a commitment to honesty, hard work, and the pursuit of
              excellence in every program.
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </Card>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
